event,"<font face=""trebuchet ms"">Huh, I guess I'm in this wedding thing too? Well, I guess I should be happy that I'm not in a dress! I was expecting that...

column2: hackable to friends (read as: anyone who knows him) ]

column1: But this kinda reminds me--Riku, Kairi... weren't we supposed to get married before?

I guess I should get started on finding out who this is--! I've got this shoe, and a piece of paper's in it... <i>"" Luckily, this princess isn't on another island. Sucks to be you if you're Japanese, though
column2: it might just give a whole new meaning to 'shotgun wedding.' ""

column1: W-wow, that sounds pretty... violent. <s>Why me?</s> I don't know anyone that sounds like that... but there aren't that many princesses here, right? And I'm sure it'd be easy for the other person to find me, if they have the shoe I'm missing!

column2: fail post is fail since Soramuse is somewhat sleepy right now. oAo and since...probably the only wedding pics of Sora have him in a dress and I'm much too lazy to find otherwise or 'shop it, he's miraculously in a tux. :|b ]</small></font>"

column1: event,"<font face=""trebuchet ms"">LOL RELATIONSHIPS LIST. This was actually supposed to go up a pretty long time ago but I just kinda forgot. 8D

Axel: ... Not sure, really. Knows how close he is to Roxas, and hasn't fought with him during the whole time they've been on the Island... but knows how he and Riku feel about each other, so can't help but feel a little more than jealous, despite not realizing it most of the time.
Demyx: Hasn't gotten the chance to talk to him much, but at least they've formed a truce as long as he doesn't attack first. Should get along well once they actually start interacting more. XD

Kairi: Loves her a lot, as she's his ""light"" and all. Of course, loves her as much as they both love Riku--hey, they're the OT3, right? Seriously concerned about her recent disappearance, and worries about her constantly.
Larxene: Was getting on fairly good ground with her before her reappearance
column2: not so sure now. Pretty sure the worst she'll do is taunt unless she gets seriously pissed off.

column1: Marluxia: Doesn't know, really. He doesn't seem to have changed at all since the last time he was seen, which is kind of annoying. Fed up and confused with his obsession to make Sora his slave. .___.
Riku: Possibly the only reason why Sora is bi. 8D
column2: Has known him forever, and even even forgave him for all that stuff he'd done in KH1, since it was for Kairi's sake and all. Still loves him more than anyone else--well, 'cept Kairi, they're tied. &hearts

column1: Roxas: because stfu they talk off-screen in my mind Sora's Nobody, of course. Whenever they talk, it's usually just casual conversation, since... well, it's kinda awkward talking to yourself butnotrly, yeah? If anything, feels sympathetic for him--really hurt that it's impossible for him to get his heart back, because of Sora, and at the same time, Sora'll never be truly complete since he's around too.
Xigbar: Only talked to him once, but before he left, they made a truce--whether it holds or not is up to him.

Fiona: Likes her. Thinks she's really nice and stuff, and thought it was nice of Riku to help her find a place to live and stuff. :3 If Riku's not around to help her, would be more than willing to fill in for him.
Giovanni: Ohohoho, scared of him. XD Or more freaked out, really. There's just something about him that Sora doesn't feel is right. Still thinks there's a good person deep inside, though. XD
Haine: Not sure. Doesn't talk to him all that much, so doesn't really know about him
column2: completely oblivious to him discreetly saying Sora's stupid, though. 8D
column3: However, sort of... afraid of him, after hearing that he killed Cain.

column1: Haruhi S.: Hasn't talked to her in a while, bu wants to, seeing as he's been getting closer to Yuki. If there was a person who'd totally blow the SOS-Dan's cover though... well, here you go. 8D

column3: Not really sure at this point--still sees Laharl as a friend and all, but is just a little jealous of him 'cause of all the time he spends with Riku. The rumors about the kiss didn't help at all.

column1: Luki: Sees her as a sort of younger sister, despite being the same age as her. XD
column2: Kind of freaked out about the whole LOL KNIFE thing, but will play tag to satisfy her whenever she asks. A little closer to her than Noki.

column1: Noki: Haha, same as Luki, just replace guns with knives. A little closer to Luki than her, though.
Yami no Yuugi: Considers him a friend. They never really got that far while he was explaining how to play Duel Monsters, and wants to try dueling him for real some time.
Yuki: Likes her, and happy that she felt welcome when told she was a friend within like, twenty minutes of meeting each other. XD
column3: Still somewhat shocked from how she demonstrated that she was a Humanoid Interface and not human, but still considers her a friend nonetheless.</lj-cut>
